---
title: Sirloin Steak Provençal with Roasted Veggies & Garlic Aioli
description: You probably haven’t tasted steak like this before: This sirloin is seasoned with Herbs de Provence—a blend of aromatics from the south of France that includes lavender, rosemary, and tarragon. Together, the meat and aromatics create some truly extraordinary flavors that feel right at home next to the dynamic sides—those would be roasted potatoes and asparagus, a rich pan sauce, and a dollop of garlic aioli.
